      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m honestly so sad to let this beauty go, but it\u2019s time for someone else to enjoy it! This car is a total gem and has been pampered since day one\u2014it looks and drives like it just rolled off the showroom floor. No scratches, no smells, just pure perfection. If you\u2019ve been looking for a ride that\u2019s been treated like royalty, you\u2019ve found it! Let\u2019s get you behind the wheel!",
